the flag was clipped on upside down.\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Viewers immediately spotted the major blunder.\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 1017, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Those who managed to stay awake during the Opening Ceremonies were treated to the Olympic flag being flown upside down,\\\" one social media user wrote.\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Oh no.\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1178, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They hung the Olympic flag upside down,\\\" a second person spotted.\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1244, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The big spectacle was washed out by the weather, the display was cringe & to top it all off the Olympic flag was hoisted upside down at the zenith of it allThis event is like a microcosm of modern France, an utter shamblespic.twitter.com/eZeyCrIXRQ  Another joked: \\\"If you are having a bad day at work, it could be worse.\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1567, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1443, \"end\": 1449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9964540348774797, \"rank\": 0.003510951504802684, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You could be the flag team that hoisted the Olympic flag upside down at the opening ceremony.\\\"\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1662, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A fourth social media described the event as a \\\"shambles\\\".\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1722, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The big spectacle was washed out by the weather, the display was cringe & to top it all off the Olympic flag was hoisted upside down at the zenith of it all,\\\" they wrote.\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1895, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The flag appeared to have been folded the whole time, so the officials were unaware.\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 1981, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But that was not the only issue.\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 2015, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Opening Ceremony kicked off under dark skies, with the threat of wet weather eventually turning into a nightmare as rain fell on spectators and athletes.\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2174, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2021, \"end\": 2037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.9999649680332344, \"rank\": 3.5019071582391786e-05, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France had decided it would host the event outside a stadium for the first time, which showcased the city of Paris and its famous landmarks.\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2316, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2176, \"end\": 2182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9964540348774797, \"rank\": 0.003510951504802684, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 2285, \"end\": 2290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.014910294841194e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, some viewers struggled to watch it on television.\", \"from\": 2318, \"to\": 2376, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The sound from this opening ceremony is terrible.\", \"from\": 2378, \"to\": 2428, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The rain was louder than any of the music at one point,\\\" one social media user wrote.\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2514, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This was the most pathetic opening ceremony of any Olympics I have ever witnessed just stupid and God showed his displeasure by pouring rain,\\\" a viewer said.\", \"from\": 2516, \"to\": 2674, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The City of Light sparkles in an unforgettable Opening Ceremony.Read more \\u00e2\\u017e\\u00a1\\u00ef\\u00b8\\u008fhttps://t.co/ULKPnCizgS#AllezAUS|@Sportscraft|#VolleyAustralia  Others loved seeing it changed up.\", \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2854, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Really different, a bit bonkers, the rain, all the boats, the painting flame thing to start, even the 90s euro dance music, the water horse, Rafa!, Celine, and the balloon flame.\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 3035, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2998, \"end\": 3002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafah\", \"score\": 0.9999275919758165, \"rank\": 7.241270756407085e-05, \"text\": \"Rafa\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Well done France.\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3053, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3046, \"end\": 3052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9964540348774797, \"rank\": 0.003510951504802684, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We will not forget this opening ceremony for sure,\\\" one person said.\", \"from\": 3054, \"to\": 3122, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Macron was not kidding.\", \"from\": 3124, \"to\": 3148, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3125, \"end\": 3131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 0.9999999856522664, \"rank\": 1.4347637459628053e-08, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This opening ceremony was incredible.\", \"from\": 3149, \"to\": 3186, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a total sensory overload, even with it pouring down rain,\\\" another added.\", \"from\": 3187, \"to\": 3267, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While it was a unique experience for all involved, athletes on boats and spectators lining the River Seine were left to scramble for their umbrellas and ponchos.\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3430, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3364, \"end\": 3375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most of the 80 Australian competitors decided to brave the rain and were left drenched from head to toe before arriving for the formalities at the Eiffel Tower.\", \"from\": 3432, \"to\": 3592, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3447, \"end\": 3457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.994009310311688, \"rank\": 0.00576305151834419, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rain fell for the majority of the Opening Ceremony.\", \"from\": 3594, \"to\": 3645, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3628, \"end\": 3644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.9999649680332344, \"rank\": 3.5019071582391786e-05, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our Apps\", \"from\": 3647, \"to\": 3655, \"entities\": []}]}"